# ALSAKKAF HOLDING GROUP - repository ignore rules
# Purpose: keep regenerated Atlas Runtime outputs out of git noise.
# Atlas_Output reports are rebuilt by atlas.py on every run and are not
# official records; the README and .gitkeep placeholders stay tracked.

# Generated Atlas Runtime reports
01_Holding_Company/08_Reports/Atlas_Output/**/*.md
!01_Holding_Company/08_Reports/Atlas_Output/**/README.md
!01_Holding_Company/08_Reports/Atlas_Output/**/.gitkeep*
!01_Holding_Company/08_Reports/Atlas_Output/**/.gitkeep_readme.txt

# Python bytecode caches (created if a test imports atlas.py)
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Partner Runtime and Department Supervisor local state (regenerated on every
# run: approval queues, memory DB, logs, draft outputs, daily plans)
09_AI_Systems/02_Tools/Partner_Runtime/Runtime_State/
09_AI_Systems/02_Tools/Department_Supervisor/Supervisor_State/
